                                                String.format("Unexpected end of segment at %d in %s", mutationStart, statusTracker.errorContext),
                                                CommitLogReadErrorReason.EOF,
                                                statusTracker.tolerateErrorsInSection)))
                {
                    statusTracker.requestTermination();
